snippet.title: Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back [GB] - Real Time Longplay (No death)
snippet.description:
This is a, no commentary, Longplay of Star Wars - The Empire Strikes Back for Game Boy. Decent game that accurately follows the movie. All Forces/1UPs/Health/Power collected. No death run. 

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Game is played by me in one go. No save states/cheats have been used. Recorded in VBA23.2.

Please note I uploaded it just for fun, no intention to compete anyone.
